The '''Gotha tramway network''' forms part of the [[public transport]] system in [[Gotha (town)|Gotha]], in the [[States of Germany|federal state]] of [[Thuringia]], [[Germany]].

Opened in 1894, the network is currently operated by Th<U+00FC>ringerwaldbahn und Stra<U+00DF>enbahn Gotha GmbH (TWSB).

